      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. The exterior has minor scratches and light wear consistent with normal use, but no significant dents or paint damage. The interior is well-maintained with some light wear on high-contact surfaces, but upholstery and trim are intact and functional. Mechanically, the car runs well with no known issues.",
